### Welcome to PUCSD Pages.
This is a landing site to start giving back initiative. PUCSD Alumni of Batch'94 will start few activities to engage current students.

### Mentorship Programme 
We believe with a little help and guidance many students will achieve lot more. We had support of our seniors who guided us. We offer mentor-ship programme to help those who feel they can talk to someone.  

Goto [Mentorship_Programme](https://kiranmak.github.io/landingpage/pages/html/mentorship.html).
